  "title": "refactor: rename all references to widgetOptions as widgetParams",
  "body": "The two terms were used interchangeably, mostly in comments and in function arguments. There's now only `TWidgetOptions` in the Widget generic, which isn't widgetParams\r\n\r\nBREAKING CHANGE: if you're using experimental-typescript and importing a type of the form `...WidgetOptions` (eg. replace `HitsWidgetOptions` with `HitsWidgetParams`)\r\n\r\n",
